Hi All,

Does nodeSDK provides any api's which accepts chaincodeid and gives the peer and member details of particular transaction?
<@U1WUAQJVC> Responded on the other channel… no I don’t know of any API that does anything similar to what you are describing. But can you be more specific on what you’re trying to achieve? Thanks!

Hi <@U0PU2N50V> we are working on resolving the issue with the documentation. For now, please access it here: <https://jimthematrix.github.io/modules/_src_hfc_.html>
